---
import AppShell from "../layouts/AppShell.astro";

const title = "Precios · SkillAtlas";
---

<AppShell title={title}>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden" data-pricing-page>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div
        class="absolute -top-24 left-1/2 h-96 w-[min(80rem,120vw)] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-indigo-200/50 via-violet-200/40 to-rose-200/45 dark:from-indigo-600/20 dark:via-violet-600/15 dark:to-rose-600/15 blur-3xl"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-80 w-80 translate-x-1/4 translate-y-1/4 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br from-sky-200/40 to-transparent dark:from-sky-500/10 blur-3xl"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-14 md:space-y-20">
      <div
        class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200/90 dark:border-amber-500/35 bg-amber-50/95 dark:bg-amber-950/35 px-4 py-3 md:px-5 md:py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:items-start sm:gap-4 shadow-sm"
        role="status"
      >
        <span
          class="shrink-0 inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-amber-500/20 dark:bg-amber-400/15 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200 text-lg font-bold"
          aria-hidden="true">!</span>
        <div class="min-w-0 space-y-1">
          <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-950 dark:text-amber-100">
            <span data-i18n="pricing.warningTitle">Importante · Precios en revisión</span>
          </p>
          <p class="m-0 text-sm text-amber-900/90 dark:text-amber-100/85 leading-relaxed">
            <span data-i18n="pricing.warningBody">Las cantidades mostradas son orientativas y aún no han sido cerradas comercialmente. Los importes y las condiciones pueden cambiar antes de activar cobros.</span>
          </p>
          <p class="m-0 text-sm text-amber-900/85 dark:text-amber-100/80 leading-relaxed mt-2">
            <span data-i18n="pricing.warningPatreon">En la mesa de diseño también…</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <header class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 pt-2 md:pt-4">
        <p
          class="m-0 inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/70 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
        >
          <span data-i18n="pricing.heroEyebrow">SkillAtlas</span>
        </p>
        <h1
          class="m-0 text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 leading-[1.12]"
        >
          <span data-i18n="pricing.heroTitle">Planes claros para organizar tu conocimiento y tu portfolio.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="m-0 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          <span data-i18n="pricing.heroSubtitle">Invitaciones limitadas hoy. Precios pensados para profesionales que quieren consistencia, no solo otro tablero vacío.</span>
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 pt-1">
          <span
            id="pricing-billing-label"
            class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
            data-i18n="pricing.billingLabel">Facturación</span>
          <div
            role="group"
            aria-labelledby="pricing-billing-label"
            class="inline-flex rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-100/90 dark:bg-gray-900/90 p-1 gap-0.5"
          >
            <button
              type="button"
              data-pricing-period="month"
              class="rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 transition-colors bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 shadow-sm"
              aria-pressed="true"
            >
              <span data-i18n="pricing.billingMonthly">Mensual</span>
            </button>
            <button
              type="button"
              data-pricing-period="year"
              class="rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
              aria-pressed="false"
            >
              <span data-i18n="pricing.billingYearly">Anual</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 lg:gap-6 items-stretch">
        <!-- Starter -->
        <article
          data-pricing-card
          data-price-month="0"
          data-price-year="0"
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 flex flex-col shadow-sm"
        >
          <div class="space-y-1 pb-4 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/80">
            <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.starterName">Starter</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.starterDesc">Para la primera fase de adopción: mapa de habilidades y portfolio coherente.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="py-5">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1.5 flex-wrap">
              <span class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-pricing-amount
                >0,00&nbsp;€</span
              >
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.perMonth"
                >/mes</span
              >
            </div>
            <p
              class="mt-2 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed min-h-8"
              data-show-on="month"
              data-i18n="pricing.noteStarterMonth"
            >
              Acceso por invitación
            </p>
            <p
              class="mt-2 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed min-h-8 hidden"
              data-show-on="year"
              data-i18n="pricing.noteStarterYear"
            >
              Acceso por invitación
            </p>
          </div>
          <ul class="m-0 p-0 list-none space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 flex-1">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.starterF1">Tecnologías, conceptos y proyectos</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.starterF2">Portfolio con sesión</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.starterF3">Evidencias enlazadas y ordenadas</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/request-access"
            class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 no-underline transition-colors"
          >
            <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaPlan">Solicitar acceso</span>
          </a>
        </article>

        <!-- Pro -->
        <article
          data-pricing-card
          data-price-month="4.99"
          data-price-year="3.99"
          class="relative rounded-2xl border-2 border-indigo-300/80 dark:border-indigo-500/40 bg-white/90 dark:bg-gray-950/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 flex flex-col shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/10 dark:shadow-indigo-500/5 lg:scale-[1.02] z-1"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-600 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white shadow-md"
          >
            <span data-i18n="pricing.proBadge">Recomendado</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1 pb-4 border-b border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-950/60 pt-2">
            <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.proName">Pro</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.proDesc">Profundidad y presentación cuando ya publicas en serio.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="py-5">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1.5 flex-wrap">
              <span class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-pricing-amount
                >€4,99</span
              >
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.perMonth"
                >/mes</span
              >
            </div>
            <p
              class="mt-2 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed min-h-8"
              data-show-on="month"
              data-i18n="pricing.notePaidMonth"
            >
              Por mes · IVA si aplica
            </p>
            <p
              class="mt-2 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed min-h-8 hidden"
              data-show-on="year"
              data-i18n="pricing.notePaidYear"
            >
              Equivalente mensual · facturación anual · ahorra frente a mensual
            </p>
          </div>
          <ul class="m-0 p-0 list-none space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 flex-1">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.proF1">Todo lo de Starter</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.proF2">Plantillas de salida y exportación avanzada (roadmap)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.proF3">Prioridad en nuevas funciones</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/request-access"
            class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-linear-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-600 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white no-underline hover:opacity-95 transition-opacity shadow-md"
          >
            <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaPlan">Solicitar acceso</span>
          </a>
        </article>

        <!-- Team -->
        <article
          data-pricing-card
          data-price-month="9.99"
          data-price-year="7.99"
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 flex flex-col shadow-sm"
        >
          <div class="space-y-1 pb-4 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/80">
            <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.teamName">Team</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.teamDesc">Cuando varias personas comparten estándar de documentación.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="py-5">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1.5 flex-wrap">
              <span class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-pricing-amount
                >€9,99</span
              >
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.perMonth"
                >/mes</span
              >
            </div>
            <p
              class="mt-2 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed min-h-8"
              data-show-on="month"
              data-i18n="pricing.notePaidMonth"
            >
              Por mes · IVA si aplica
            </p>
            <p
              class="mt-2 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed min-h-8 hidden"
              data-show-on="year"
              data-i18n="pricing.notePaidYear"
            >
              Equivalente mensual · facturación anual · ahorra frente a mensual
            </p>
          </div>
          <ul class="m-0 p-0 list-none space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 flex-1">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.teamF1">Todo lo de Pro</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.teamF2">Facturación centralizada</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <span data-i18n="pricing.teamF3">Canal de soporte dedicado</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/request-access"
            class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 no-underline transition-colors"
          >
            <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaPlan">Solicitar acceso</span>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Comparativa -->
      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/60 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="px-5 py-4 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/80">
          <h2 class="m-0 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
            <span data-i18n="pricing.compareTitle">Comparativa rápida</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full min-w-lg text-sm border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="text-left text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/80">
                <th class="py-3 px-5 font-medium" data-i18n="pricing.compareFeature">Funcionalidad</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-center">Starter</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-center text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                  <span data-i18n="pricing.comparePro">Pro</span>
                </th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-center">Team</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/60">
                <td class="py-3 px-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.compareRowPortfolio">
                  Portfolio y perfil público
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/60">
                <td class="py-3 px-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.compareRowProjects">
                  Proyectos con evidencias
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/60">
                <td class="py-3 px-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.compareRowConcepts">
                  Conceptos por tecnología
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/60">
                <td class="py-3 px-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.compareRowCv">
                  CV & exportación
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">❌</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareNo">No incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.compareRowShareToken">
                  Enlace público de portfolio (token)
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">❌</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareNo">No incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-lg">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">✅</span>
                  <span class="sr-only" data-i18n="pricing.compareYes">Incluido</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQs -->
      <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-3">
        <h2 class="m-0 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 text-center">
          <span data-i18n="pricing.faqsTitle">Preguntas frecuentes</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/60 px-4 py-3 open:shadow-sm">
            <summary
              class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between gap-2"
            >
              <span data-i18n="pricing.faq1Q">¿Puedo usar SkillAtlas sin pagar ahora?</span>
              <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.faq1A">Durante el acceso anticipado por invitación, el plan Starter cubre el núcleo del producto. Los planes de pago se activarán cuando abramos la facturación.</span>
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/60 px-4 py-3 open:shadow-sm">
            <summary
              class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between gap-2"
            >
              <span data-i18n="pricing.faq2Q">¿Qué incluye el plan Team?</span>
              <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.faq2A">Prioridad en soporte, preparado para varios perfiles en la misma cuenta de facturación y necesidades de alineación en equipo. Detalles concretos se acuerdan al contratar.</span>
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/60 px-4 py-3 open:shadow-sm">
            <summary
              class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between gap-2"
            >
              <span data-i18n="pricing.faq3Q">¿Hay permanencia?</span>
              <span class="text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              <span data-i18n="pricing.faq3A">No pensamos en permanencias forzadas. En la facturación anual aplicamos descuento por compromiso; si cambian tus prioridades, podrás ajustar el ciclo según las condiciones vigentes en ese momento.</span>
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <section
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-linear-to-br from-gray-50 to-indigo-50/80 dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-indigo-950/40 p-8 md:p-10 text-center space-y-4"
      >
        <h2 class="m-0 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
          <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaTitle">¿Listo para ordenar tu stack?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="m-0 mx-auto max-w-lg text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
